BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-21T01:00:00&endDate=2026-03-23T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nPICCADILLY LINE: Saturday 21 and Sunday 22 March\, no service between Cockfosters and Uxbridge (including Friday and Saturday Night Tube). Trains will continue to run between Acton Town and Heathrow. Use METROPOLITAN LINE services between Rayners Lane and Uxbridge\, and ELIZABETH LINE services between Paddington and Heathrow. Replacement bus services operate.
DTEND:20260323T012900Z
DTSTART:20260321T010000Z
SUMMARY:Piccadilly: Part Closure
UID:c771a5a1-c2a9-43a7-952a-024d866920a7@c771.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-14T01:00:00&endDate=2026-04-14T07:00:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nPICCADILLY LINE: Saturday 14 April\, between 0100 and 0700\, no service between Hyde Park Corner and Acton Town. Replacement bus service PL1 operates between Green Park and Acton Town via Hyde Park Corner\, Knightsbridge\, South Kensington\, Gloucester Road\, Earls Court\, Hammersmith (for Barons Court) and Turnham Green (Bath Road).
DTEND:20260414T070000Z
DTSTART:20260414T010000Z
